quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  11,50,"N’abantu bo mu bwoko bw’aba Adi twaboherereje umuvandimwe wabo Hudu, aravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimugaragire Allah! Nta yindi mana mufite ikwiye gusengwa itari we. Nta kindi muri cyo uretse kuba abahimbyi b’ibinyoma"
  11,51,"Yemwe bantu banjye! (Kubagezaho ubutumwa) nta gihembo mbibasabira, ahubwoigihembo cyanjye ngiteze ku wandemye. Ese ntimutekereza"
  11,52,"Yemwe bantu banjye! Nimusabe imbabazi Nyagasani wanyu maze munamwicuzeho; (ibyo nimubikora) azaboherereza imvura nyinshi (izeza imyaka yanyu), anabongerere imbaraga ku zo musanganywe. Kandi muramenye ntimuzirengagize (ibyo mbabwira) ngo mube inkozi z’ibibi"
  11,53,"Baravuga bati \"Yewe Hudu! Nta kimenyetso utuzaniye, kandi nta n’ubwo tuzigera tureka imana zacukubera ibyo utubwira, ndetse nta n’ubwo duteze kukwemera"
  11,54,"Icyo twavuga nuko zimwe mu mana zacu zaguteje ibyago (kuko ubuza abantu kuzisenga). Aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ntanze Allah ho umuhamya, kandi na mwe nimube abahamya ko rwose nitandukanyije n’ibyo mubangikanya musenga"
  11,55,Bitari we (Allah). Ngaho nimuncurire imigambi mibisha mwese kandi ntimundindirize
  11,56,"Mu by’ukuri, njye niringiye Allah, Nyagasani wanjye akaba na Nyagasani wanyu. Nta kiremwa na kimwe Allah atagenga. Rwose, Nyagasani wanjye ni we ufite inzira igororotse"
  11,57,"Ubwo nimutera umugongo (ukuri, mumenye ko) njye namaze kubagezaho ubutumwa nahawe, kandiNyagasani wanjye azabasimbuza abandi bantu, ndetse ntacyo muzamutwara. Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanjye ni Umurinzi wa byose"
  11,58,"Ubwo isezerano ryacu (ryo guhana abigometse) ryasohoraga, twarokoye Hudu n’abemeye hamwe na we ku bw'impuhwe ziduturutseho, maze tubakiza ibihano bikomeye"
  11,59,"Abo bari (abantu bo) mu bwoko bw’aba Adi. Bahakanye ibimenyetso bya Nyagasani wabo, bigomeka ku ntumwa ze, banakurikira amategeko ya buri mwibone wese w’igomeke"
  11,60,"Kandi bakurikijwe umuvumo muri iyi si ndetse (uzanabakurikirana) no ku munsi w'imperuka. Nta gushidikanya ko mu by’ukuri, ubwoko bw’aba Adi bwahakanye Nyagasani wabwo, kandi ko ubwoko bw’aba Adi, aribo bantu ba Hudu, bwarimbutse"